snippet.title: TransOcean 2: Rivals - feature trailer
snippet.description:
Take a first look into the world of TransOcean 2: Rivals with this first feature trailer!

The vessels have been refueled, the cargo has been loaded and ambitious ship owners can hardly wait to finally cast off with TransOcean 2: Rivals. Developer Deck13 Hamburg and publisher astragon Entertainment are therefore more than happy to announce the official worldwide release date of the challenging economic strategy simulation today: TransOcean 2: Rivals will be available for PC and Mac starting May 11th, 2016! 

For more information, please visit us on our website: www.transocean2.com or on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TransOceanGame
